adithonline\/2015\/03\/07\/sabr-iman-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":31994,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Conviction: Patience half of faith, certainty all of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Alqamah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cPatience is half of faith and conviction is faith in its entirety.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 9083 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u00a0\u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0646\u0650\u0635\u0652\u0641\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0643\u064f\u0644\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064f 9083\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/20\/salah-ummah-zuhd\/","url_meta":{"origin":31994,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Righteousness in temperance, destruction in worldly hope","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe rightness in the beginning of this nation was by renouncing the world and attaining conviction. The destruction in the end of it is by miserliness and vain hopes.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 52\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36307,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/24\/fasad-bukhl-aml\/","url_meta":{"origin":31994,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Bukhl: Corruption of Ummah by miserliness, worldly hopes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe beginning of righteousness in this nation is by conviction and temperance, and the beginning of its corruption by is miserliness and vain hopes.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 10350 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/17\/call-upon-allah-with-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":31994,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Conviction: Call upon Allah with certainty, without distraction","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCall upon Allah with certainty that He will answer you. Know that Allah will not answer the supplication of an unmindful and distracted heart.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3479 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \